<h1>No more public transport jungle!</h1>
<p>The 9-Euro-Ticket has proven, that people are hindered from freely travelling
    not only by high prices, but also by the hard to navigate web of German
    public transport networks.</p>
<p>We demand the abolition of the regional transport networks and propose the
    introduction of ONE big national public transport network.</p>
<p>With just one "Monatsticket" you should be able to take any region train,
    tram, subway, bus or commmuter-ferry in the entire country.</p>
<h2>Do you agree?</h2>
<h2>Then sign our petition!</h2>
<form method="POST">
    <label for="firstName" class="formLabel">First Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="firstName" id="firstName" {{#if signingFailed}}{{#if firstName}}value="{{firstName}}" {{else}} class="red-border"{{/if}}{{/if}}/>
    <label for="lastName" class="formLabel">Last Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="lastName" id="lastName" {{#if signingFailed}}{{#if lastName}}value="{{lastName}}" {{else}} class="red-border"{{/if}}{{/if}}/>
    <input
        type="text"
        name="signatureURL"
        id="signatureURL"
        class="invisible"
        
    />
    <label for="sigField">Sign your name with your mouse or finger here:</label>
    <canvas width="600" height="200" id="sigField" name="sigField" class="canvas {{#if signingFailed}}{{#if signatureURL}}{{signatureURL}}{{else}}red-border{{/if}}{{/if}}"></canvas>
    <input type="submit" id="submitSignature" class="submit" value="SIGN NOW!"></input>
</form>
{{#if signingFailed}}<p class="red bold">You have not filled in all the required fields. Please check again and resubmit!</p>{{/if}}
